// tropical          : Hot & humid year-round. Rain > 1500mm. Kerala, coastal AP, Goa, Andaman
// subtropical       : Hot summers, mild winters. UP plains, Bihar, peninsular plateau, Punjab
// semiarid          : Hot & dry, 400-700mm rain. Parts of Rajasthan, Telangana, interior Maharashtra
// arid              : Very hot, very dry, <400mm rain. Rajasthan desert, Kutch
// highland          : Cool to cold, high altitude. Himachal, Uttarakhand, NE hills, Nilgiris, Coorg
// humid_subtropical : Hot humid summers, cool winters. Bengal, Assam, Odisha, NE plains

